&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-TAO-DOWNTOWN-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8359&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-TAO-DOWNTOWN-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;NYC- TAO DOWNTOWN- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;133&quot; height=&quot;65&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Tao Downtown Nightclub is a hidden lounge below Tao Downtown restaurant, with a separate entrance adding to the exclusivity. A dramatic staircase leads guests to a chic cavern with sexy lighting, industrial elements and Asian-influenced details. Music is open format, keeping a very chic international clientele dancing, drinking and socializing into the wee hours. Upscale trendy attire &amp;#8211; dress to impress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Tao Downtown via email only at dinersclubnyc@taogroup.com to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention that the booking is for a reservation at TAO Downtown New York.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for 2 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A credit card will not be required for general reservations but may be required for special events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Upscale, trendy. No sneakers, hats, boots, athletic wear, or shorts for gentlemen. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

